                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2017-10-13T13:00:20.138+02:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="a480381"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="gotomarket/components/content/richtext"
                                text="&lt;p>Increasing international mobility creates new business opportunities as consumers appreciate knowing the cost of foreign ATM withdrawals or international payments in their home currency. Therefore we, together with FEXCO, have introduced WL Dynamic Currency Conversion (DCC). This offers full insight into the foreign exchange rate applied and the cost of a transaction in the home currency.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>Our end-to-end solution includes exchange rates provision, transaction processing, settlement and reconciliation. It enables you to offer international cardholders the benefits of paying in home currency, having full transparency and reducing foreign exchange risks through instant conversion. Moreover, it will create an additional revenue stream and an enhancement of your services to merchants and on ATM devices, thereby strengthening your competitive position.&lt;/p>&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </column1>
                    </grid>
                </items>
            </section>
